# ---------------------------------------------------------------
# Kubernetes Plain Secrets
# NOTE: ExternalSecret manifests (k8s/secrets/*.yaml) are safe to
# commit because they only reference GCP Secret Manager paths.
# This rule is a safety net — if someone accidentally creates a
# plain Secret yaml, it won't be tracked.
# Plain secrets look like: kind: Secret  (not ExternalSecret)
# ---------------------------------------------------------------
# k8s/secrets/plain-*.yaml   # Uncomment if you add plain-secret files
